data.description: Nestled on three picturesque acres beneath the majestic Grand Mesa in Cedaredge, CO, this mid-century modern gem invites you to embrace the tranquility of mountain living. With three bedrooms and two baths, this haven offers a serene retreat just moments from downtown Cedaredge and Delta. Gaze upon the breathtaking vistas of the San Juan and Elk Mountain ranges from your front porch, while a nearby creek serenades you to sleep with its soothing melody. Embrace the elements with open windows, letting in the gentle breeze from the Mesa, ensuring cool summers without the need for air conditioning. This eco-friendly sanctuary boasts solar panels atop the heated garage/shop, granting you electricity independence from April through November. Cozy up in cool weather with electric radiant heating and an original wood-burning stove, or unwind in the backyard jacuzzi, included for your relaxation. Work effortlessly from home with lightning-fast fiber optic internet connectivity. Revel in the abundance of wildlife, while a fenced garden ensures your harvest remains exclusively yours. In the spring, delight in picking fresh peaches, plums, pears, and apples from the fruit trees adorning your front yard. Welcome to your slice of paradise, where modern comfort meets natural beauty.
